            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6">
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
                <strong>¿Estás seguro de que deseas guardar la asistencia?</strong>
            </p>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-4">
                Una vez guardada, la asistencia <strong>no podrá ser modificada</strong> a menos que te comuniques con un administrador.
            </p>
            <div class="bg-yellow-50 border border-yellow-200 rounded-lg p-3 mb-4">
                <p class="text-xs text-yellow-800">
                    <svg class="w-4 h-4 inline mr-1" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                        <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M8.257 3.099c.765-1.36 2.722-1.36 3.486 0l5.58 9.92c.75 1.334-.213 2.98-1.742 2.98H4.42c-1.53 0-2.493-1.646-1.743-2.98l5.58-9.92zM11 13a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zm-1-8a1 1 0 00-1 1v3a1 1 0 002 0V6a1 1 0 00-1-1z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                    </svg>
                    Asegúrate de que todos los estados estén correctos antes de continuar.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="px-6 pb-6 flex gap-3">
            <button type="button"
                    onclick="cerrarModalConfirmacion()"
                    class="flex-1 px-6 py-3 bg-gray-200 text-gray-700 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-300 transition-all font-medium">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 inline mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12"></path>
                </svg>
                Revisar de Nuevo
            </button>
            <button type="button"
                    onclick="confirmarGuardarAsistencia()"
                    class="flex-1 px-6 py-3 bg-gradient-to-r from-green-500 to-green-600 text-white rounded-lg hover:from-green-600 hover:to-green-700 transition-all font-medium">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 inline mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
